<root>
  <FromEmail></FromEmail>
  <ToEmail></ToEmail>
  <Subject>Welcome to SSE</Subject>
  <Body bgcolor="#F7F7F7" text="#898989">
    <!--<style> 
      @media only screen and (max-width:600px){
          #bodyCont{width:100% !important}
      } 
    </style>-->
    <table id="bodyCont"  width="600" style="max-width:100%" BORDER="0" CELLPADDING="0" CELLSPACING="0" ALIGN="center">
      <tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
        <td valign="middle" align="middle" width="200" height="85">
          <a href="http://[$Domain]" target="_blank" title="SSE">
            <img src="[$CDNBaseUrl]/Content/Images/EmailTemplates/sse-email-logo.png" border="0" alt="SSE" class="sse-logo" style="display:block;" />
          </a>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <img src="[$CDNBaseUrl]/Content/Images/EmailTemplates/neon-house-email-banner.png" alt="SSE; Energy | Home Services | Phone and Broadband" title="SSE; Energy | Home Services | Phone and Broadband" border="0" style="width:100%; display:inline-block" />
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="max-width:600px; padding-top:20px; background-color:white;">
          <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center">
            <tr>
              <td colspan="3" height="25"></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td width="40"></td>
              <td style="color:#616161; font-size:16px; padding:0; line-height:20px; font-family:Calibri, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">
                <span style="font-size:20px; line-height:24px; font-weight:bold;color:#004687;">Hi [$FIRSTNAME],</span>
                <br />
                <br />Thanks for choosing the [$SELECTEDPRODUCTTITLE] tariff. It's great that you're joining us.
                <br />
                <br/>
                <span style="font-size:18px; line-height:24px; font-weight:bold;color: #004687;">What happens next?</span>
                <br />
                <br />
                You'll receive a Welcome pack shortly with all you need to know about your tariff, including terms and conditions, payment details and other useful information.
                <br />
                <br />
                We'll switch your energy supply to us within 21 days, so there’s no need to contact your old supplier. We'll be in touch about your opening meter readings.
                <br />
                <br />
                <span><a style="text-decoration:none;font-size:18px; line-height:25px; font-weight:bold;color: #2B7BB9;" href="https://sse.co.uk/help/energy/switching" target="_blank">About your switch to SSE</a> </span>
                <br/>                
                <span><a style="text-decoration:none;font-size:18px; line-height:32px; font-weight:bold;color: #2B7BB9;" href="https://sse.co.uk/help/energy/meters/how-to-read-your-meter" target="_blank">How to read your gas or electricity meter</a> </span>
                <br/>
                <br/>
                <span style="font-size:18px; line-height:24px; font-weight:bold;color: #004687;">Anything else?</span>
                <br/>
                <br/>
                We'll let you know how your switch is going at every step. Meanwhile, feel free to <a style="text-decoration:none;font-weight:bold;color: #2B7BB9;" href="https://sse.co.uk/help/contact-us" target="_blank" >get in touch</a> if you have any questions. We'll be happy to help.
                <br/>
                <br/>
                <br/>
                <span style="font-size:18px; line-height:24px;">Welcome to SSE!</span>
                <br />
                <br />
                <span>The Team at SSE</span>
                <br/>
                <strong>SSE Customer Services</strong>
                <br />               
              </td>
              <td width="40"></td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td  height="124" bgcolor="#ffffff">
          <img src="[$CDNBaseUrl]/Content/Images/EmailTemplates/email-footer.png" alt="SSE; Energy | Home Services | Phone and Broadband" title="SSE; Energy | Home Services | Phone and Broadband" border="0" style="width:100%; display:inline-block" />
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td height="35" width="100%"  align="left" valign="middle" style="color:#002961; font-size:14px; padding:0; line-height:18px; font-family:Calibri, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">
          This is an automated response. Please don’t reply to this email.
        </td>
      </tr>
